{"tid":1630352,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"吳 x 倩小朋友 係215 X跌咗銀包","createTime":"2019-10-06T12:11:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T20:40:02.000Z","uid":140302,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"46a4aaabbc4db09883d8d7994453927c795ad761","tid":1630352,"uid":140302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:11:21.000Z","msg":"幫你執返俾咗巴士司機佢話會擺喺總站<br />\n<br />\n光復香港時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da2891b567a434b6ff7d127bcaf2267aab3713d1","tid":1630352,"uid":140302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:12:08.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"037cebd9d3787d49ae96b7f140b135ac70bdd77b","tid":1630352,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:13:04.000Z","msg":"大家知唔知道宜家外國人點諗勇武<br />\n勇武要大家backup 啊！<br />\n<br />\n正式宣布：文宣洗地開始［行動po求置頂］<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630198\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630198</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ef75f95f563fd9335240157da6b570d510ac24bc","tid":1630352,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:13:15.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"783dce7a844d20f1483788de196d7424e627f7bf","tid":1630352,"uid":245670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:19:12.000Z","msg":"巴打好有愛<br />\n<br />\n我真係跪求咁多位前線勇武巴打   可唔可以唔好再做哩樣嘢！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630109\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630109</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"80e2281bc94a3136fecc7803fdd3dd651a3039f6","tid":1630352,"uid":140302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:24:39.000Z","msg":"隨心推多幾下"},{"pid":"585a9d3e2b8e8401f0909690ac62bbffc4f82c53","tid":1630352,"uid":48965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:26:28.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5accd7479828fa89d4acfda72b493de2190aec8a","tid":1630352,"uid":140302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:35:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f3a604d41ac12724217cab3ac18863479ea32199","tid":1630352,"uid":140302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:39:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9818dcef31ca413ff3d9126bcade5ce9777828e6","tid":1630352,"uid":140302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:54:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eb4df13f431fef33a85e50b7824cabac594e4217","tid":1630352,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:56:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"69cfd73eda6b79b983c05c3338e819af2ad6db46","tid":1630352,"uid":140302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"